I did what I was told.

505
00:33:07.208 --> 00:33:08.792
I... I just want to go home.

506
00:33:10.083 --> 00:33:11.167
Yeah. 'course you do.

507
00:33:13.500 --> 00:33:14.583
You know what?

508
00:33:16.500 --> 00:33:17.958
I think that can be arranged.

509
00:33:18.042 --> 00:33:19.583
[breathing deeply]

510
